[[File:CES_2012_-_Sony_4K_camera_(6764176429).jpg|缩略图]]'''4K解析度'''（'''{{lang|en|4K resolution}}'''），或簡稱作'''4K'''，是指[[显示器|显示器]]或顯示內容的水平（横向）显示大约4096[[像素|像素]]左右的[[分辨率|分辨率]]<ref>{{cite book |last=Goulekas |first=Karen |date=2001 |title=Visual Effects in a Digital World |url=https://archive.org/details/visualeffectsind0000goul |publisher=[[摩根·考夫曼|摩根·考夫曼]] |page=[https://archive.org/details/visualeffectsind0000goul/page/587 587] |isbn=9780080520711 |author-link=Karen Goulekas |quote=4K resolution: A general term referring to any digital image containing an X resolution of approximately 4096 pixels. }}</ref>，亦即横向解像度達到4000[[像素|像素]]的級別、而纵向解像度達到2000像素的級別<ref name="The Ultimate Guide to 4K Ultra HD">{{Citation | url = http://www.ultrahdtv.net/the-ultimate-guide-to-4k-and-8k-ultra-hd/ | title = The Ultimate Guide to 4K Ultra HD | newspaper = Ultra HDTV Magazine | accessdate = 2013-10-27 | archive-date = 2015-03-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150324181932/http://www.ultrahdtv.net/the-ultimate-guide-to-4k-and-8k-ultra-hd/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

現時在數位電視及數位攝影的領域裡，[[数字电视|數位電視]]和[[数字电影|數位電影]]通常使用几种不同的4K分辨率。在电视和消费的媒体中，3840×2160（4K [[超高画质电视|UHD]]）是主流的4K标准，而电影放映行业使用的是4096×2160（{{link-en|DCI|Digital Cinema Initiatives}} 4K）。

== 历史 ==
[[File:4K_resolution_sample.ogv|thumb]]
[[File:Digital_video_resolutions_(VCD_to_4K).svg|thumb]]
2003年，加拿大Dalsa公司推出一款4K级别的-{zh-cn:数字; zh-tw:數位}-电影摄影机[[Dalsa_Origin|Dalsa Origin]]，是世界上首部商业用途的4K摄像机<ref name="cfd">{{cite book |title=Cinematography for Directors: A Guide for Creative Collaboration |last=Frost |first=Jacqueline B |year=2009 |publisher=Michael Wiese Productions |isbn=1615930191 |page=199 |url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=MeQtam4PbwIC |accessdate=21 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203063217/http://books.google.com.au/books?id=MeQtam4PbwIC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[YouTube|YouTube]]在2010年7月開始提供一些4K解析度的短片供在线瀏覽，同時也允許已註冊用戶上傳超過[[1080p|1080p]]解析度的影片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://youtube-global.blogspot.com/2010/07/whats-bigger-than-1080p-4k-video-comes.html|title=What's bigger than 1080p? 4K video comes to YouTube|author=Ramesh Sarukkai|date=2010-07-09|accessdate=2010-07-09|archive-date=2011-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716174036/http://youtube-global.blogspot.com/2010/07/whats-bigger-than-1080p-4k-video-comes.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[索尼|索尼]]在2004年推出4K电影放映机<ref name="spr">{{cite web |url=http://www.projectorcentral.com/news_story_674.htm |title=Sony Unveils New "4k" Digital Cinema Projector |date=June 3, 2004 |work=Press Release |publisher=ProjectorCentral.com |accessdate=24 May 2014 |archive-date=2018-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618175226/http://www.projectorcentral.com/news_story_674.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2012年推出4K[[家庭影院|家庭影院]]电影放映机<ref name="srwf">{{cite web |url=http://www.gizmag.com/sony-vpl-vw1000es-4k-projector/22760/ |title=Sony releases world's first 4K home theater projector |author=Darren Quick |date=May 31, 2012 |work=Gizmag |accessdate=24 May 2014 |archive-date=2016-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723212435/http://www.gizmag.com/sony-vpl-vw1000es-4k-projector/22760/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== Mastered in 4K ===
索尼作為4K的重要推動者，為了應對4K電視推廣期片源稀少所產生[[先有雞還是先有蛋|雞與蛋的問題]]——即如果沒有足夠片源就沒有人會購買高價的4K設備，無法大量生產又會造成售價高昂和推廣困難——自2014年起開始推出Mastered in 4K格式的藍光光碟影片。其原理是以4K掃瞄母帶後再轉換成2K解像度的藍光光碟<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.trustedreviews.com/opinions/what-is-mastered-in-4k-and-does-it-make-a-difference |title=What is Mastered in 4K? |accessdate=2015-09-27 |archive-date=2017-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170624104447/http://www.trustedreviews.com/opinions/what-is-mastered-in-4k-and-does-it-make-a-difference |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由於部分片種拍攝時已經以4K[[攝影機|攝影機]]攝製，因此廠方聲稱以4K TV去播放這些光碟將有更出色的精細度和顏色真實效果，作為一種過渡期產品，所有傳統藍光播放器都能放映這種影片，因為其並非真實的4K原生3840*2160解析度而依然是傳統1920*1080解析度。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ultrahdtv.net/articles/mastered-in-4k/ |title=ultrahdtv.net |accessdate=2015-09-27 |archive-date=2020-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007065803/http://www.ultrahdtv.net/articles/mastered-in-4k/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

